EQUALITY OPERATORS
__________________

== vs. ===          (returns true or false value)

=== exactly         (actually always use this!)
==                  (actually never use this)

=== (does not type coersion)            '18' + 18           -> false
==  (does type coersion)                '18' + 18           -> true


!== NOT equal




